For vista users... 
1. run the game from the launcher
2. if it works, u're really lucky
3. if not, right click on launcher, properties, compatibility tab, "run as an administrator" then click OK
4. run the game as an admin
5. every time u run the game, u must switch between running the game as admin or normal user. Every two times play as admin, every two times as user :)
5. if that don't work, make the game compatible with windows XP, and then play with admin and use again :) 
6. switching for me worked every time; 
7. u should run the game in those combinations then:

Vista/admin
Vista/user
XP/admin
XP/user

... tough luck guys, one of those combinations will always work!

sometimes though, the game will start as not_full window. then u have to go to options, video and resolution... u have to switch the resolution to existing one, the game should maximize. or simply right click in taskbar on star wars, (few times, finally should work) and click maximize!!

finally, the game is ready to play :D

i know, i spoiled the fun of finding out how to rung the game for (x32) vista users, but well... sometimes i can be really selfish person :D

BTW:
